<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>👏welcome</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html,
    body {
      height: 100%;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    body {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      position: relative;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -300px;
      right: -300px;
      bottom: -300px;
      left: -300px;
      background: conic-gradient(from 180deg at 50% 50%, #12001B -97.5deg, #000000 14.05deg, #040EFF 54.01deg, #8000FF 113.42deg, #00B6B6 185.62deg, #12001B 262.5deg, #000000 374.05deg);
      filter: blur(60px) brightness(1.5);
      z-index: -1;
      animation: 30s move linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes move {
      from {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
      }

      to {
        transform: rotate(540deg);
      }
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 66px;
    }

    ol {
      padding: 66px;
    }

    li {
      margin: 6px 0;
    }

    ul {
      padding: 0 66px;
    }

    ul li {
      list-style-type: '*'
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <h1>Fake API</h1>

  <ol>
    <li>npm i</li>
    <li>使用「config-template.js」模板文件创建「config.js」</li>
    <li>npm start</li>
    <li>直接访问接口url（http://localhost:xxxx/xxxxxxxx/xxx）</li>
    <li>在配置文件夹下自动生成的文件中填写返回数据</li>
    <li>再次访问url,获得返回数据</li>
  </ol>
  <ul>
    <li>建议全局安装nodemon,若未安装请修改「package.json」中start配置</li>
  </ul>
</body>


</html>